
Linkumori (Clean URLs) -- MV3 WebRequest Firefox Add-on
========================================================

The Linkumori codebase is primarily derived from other open-source projects,
particularly the ClearURLs add-on and related projects. See THIRD-PARTY-NOTICE/
and LICENSE.md for full third-party attribution and license details.


LINKUMORI FIRST-PARTY AUTHOR
------------------------------

  Subham Mahesh
  GitHub: https://github.com/Linkumori
  Role:   Primary author and maintainer


UPSTREAM: CLEARURLS
--------------------

A large portion of the Linkumori codebase originates from or is derived from
the ClearURLs project by Kevin Röbert, used under the GNU Lesser General
Public License (LGPL) v3.0 or later.

  Kevin Röbert
  GitHub: https://github.com/ClearURLs/Addon
  Role:   Original ClearURLs author (upstream)


