MODIFICATION HISTORY
---------------------

Due to space constraints, later modifications are not tracked inline.
To view the full modification history, run:

  node linkumori-cli-tool.js

Then select "Generate Commit History". This will create a Markdown file
where you can browse who modified which files and on what date.

Note: git clone is required before running "Generate Commit History":

  git clone https://github.com/Linkumori/Linkumori-Addon-MV3-Firefox.git
